response.original_title: Girls Gone Wild: Ultimate Spring Break
response.overview: Girls Gone Wild: Best of Ultimate Spring Break, Vol. 1 captures a variety of women exposing their flesh to the camera. The DVD offers a standard full-frame transfer. The English soundtrack is rendered in Dolby Digital Stereo. There are no supplemental materials of any consequence, although fans of the Girls Gone Wild series will get what they expect.
